Values must be numeric.
Values set in the config file can be overridden by command\-line flags.
.PP
Only allowed keys are accepted.
Unknown keys produce a warning on stderr and are ignored.
.PP
The file must be owned by root (uid 0); otherwise it is rejected
entirely.
